747
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:24,210
Masuk akal.

748
00:38:41,890 --> 00:38:42,410
Apa yang kau lakukan?

749
00:38:43,490 --> 00:38:44,540
Melempari kepala Bai Jue.

750
00:38:48,100 --> 00:38:49,820
Bukankah kau bilang
tidak takut padanya?

751
00:38:50,210 --> 00:38:52,410
Bukan takut padanya,
tidak bisa kujelaskan.

752
00:38:55,690 --> 00:38:56,410
Baiklah,

753
00:38:57,100 --> 00:38:58,380
kau lihat saja pelan-pelan.

754
00:38:58,650 --> 00:38:59,210
Aku pergi dulu.

755
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:01,020
Nanti kita bertemu di gerbang.

756
00:39:02,140 --> 00:39:02,860
Kembali.

757
00:39:04,210 --> 00:39:05,210
Nanti kau tersesat.

758
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:19,440
♪Di mana dirimu♪

759
00:39:19,830 --> 00:39:22,720
♪Wajah yang belia♪

760
00:39:24,930 --> 00:39:25,730
Airnya sedikit dalam,

761
00:39:26,650 --> 00:39:27,380
