762
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:33,180
♪Perasaan dalam mata♪

763
00:39:33,210 --> 00:39:34,100
Kapan kau terbangun?

764
00:39:35,540 --> 00:39:36,170
Hari ini.

765
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:39,410
