774
00:39:56,830 --> 00:39:58,110
♪Bisa ada berapa banyak takdir♪

775
00:39:58,170 --> 00:39:59,100
Bukan aku yang mau datang,

776
00:39:59,340 --> 00:40:00,020
tetapi Yuan Qi.

777
00:40:00,930 --> 00:40:01,650
Kalau begitu, di mana Yuan Qi?

778
00:40:01,690 --> 00:40:02,720
♪Selama ribuan tahun♪

779
00:40:03,210 --> 00:40:04,210
Entah pergi ke mana.

780
00:40:04,930 --> 00:40:05,450
Tidak perlu khawatir,

781
00:40:06,450 --> 00:40:07,100
dia sering kemari,

782
00:40:07,410 --> 00:40:08,060
tidak akan hilang.

783
00:40:09,930 --> 00:40:10,690
Jelas-jelas dia...

784
00:40:11,730 --> 00:40:12,410
Kenapa kau lagi!

785
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:14,210
